In order to fully participate in the Business performance planning Partner Enablement workshop, the following steps must be completed.
An environment with Buisness performance planning installed. [Install Business performance planning](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/finance/business-performance-planning/bpp-app-install#install-the-app)
Partners have the option of utilizing a Partner Tier 2 sandbox environment OR they may utiilize a Fabric** trial license with Power BI.  **NOte:  A fabric trial license is only good for 5 weeks, so please consider the timing of the training class when signing up for the trial.  A Power BI trial instance can be used but a Power BI Pro license is prefered. 
After BPP is installed, ensure that one user is assigned the BPP Admin role, and the Dataflows maker role.
After installing BPP, install the BPP add-in.  [Install Excel Add-in](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/finance/business-performance-planning/install-excel-add)
Install Power BI desktop and ensure user has a Power BI pro license
Recommended but not requiired:  [Install Business performanc analytics](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/finance/business-performance-analytics/install-bpa)
